author: Brie Stimson
title: Malibu paddleboarder arrested for violating stay-at-home order
description: A Southern California paddleboarder was arrested Thursday for violating the statewide “Safer at Home” coronavirus order, the Los Angeles County Sheriff's Department confirmed.
content:
A Southern California paddleboarder was arrested Thursday for allegedly violating the statewide “safer at home” coronavirus order, the Los Angeles County Sheriff's Department said.
